reviewText: Wish they would do in English instead of subtitles

The first in a series of fascinating behind the scene looks at Andre's life and performances. It's a real pleasure to watch the performers interact and how the incredible productions developed. Lots of great music, too.
LOVE READING ABOUT THEIR TOUR TRAVEL LOGISTICS
I love andre Rieu, yes it is wonderful to see how Andre works behind the scenes.  He is magic over and above!
VERY PLEASED WITH THE FIRST FOUR EPISODES OF ANDRE'S LIFE IN HIS TRAVELS. ONE DOES LEARN A LITTLE MORE OF WHAT HAS OCCURRED ON THE ROAD AND BEHIND THE SCENES.
As always. pure ambrosia for the senses.
